Constraints:
- The corrected implementation must handle hash collisions gracefully without losing virtual nodes.
- It must support adding/removing the same node idempotently.
- It must maintain O(log N) lookup and O(log N) insertion/deletion per virtual node, where N is the number of virtual nodes.
- It must handle non-string keys by converting them to a canonical string representation.
